    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chinese painting technique having outline and definition, giving shading, depth, and texture to the work using ink alone.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
